Package: libcorerat-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends},
         libsertial-dev, libreflect-cpp-dev
Description: CoreRaT - C++20 real-time platform abstraction (dev headers + static lib)
 Provides the shared foundation for CommRaT: platform abstraction (threading,
 timestamps), wire message types, TiMS TCP IPC backend, and the CoreRaT router.

Package: corerat-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, systemd
Description: CoreRaT tools (corerat-router-tcp)
 TiMS-compatible TCP router for use with CommRaT and CoreRaT-based applications.
